Reagent 1：Contains 500 mL of sodium hydroxide in an aqueous solution.

Level 1 Control Kit：Contains 1x 25 mL of Negative Control (3.0 mg/dL creatinine) and 1x 25 mL of Positive Control (7.5 mg/dL creatinine) in an aqueous solution.
Level 2 Control Kit：Contains 1x 25 mL of Negative Control (15.0 mg/dL creatinine) and 1 x 25 mL of Positive Control (25.0 mg/dL creatinine) in an aqueous solution.
